something fun.

291
00:35:52,683 --> 00:35:54,351
Hawaii.

292
00:35:55,620 --> 00:35:57,254
Show me a beach.

293
00:35:58,756 --> 00:36:00,423
Boring.

294
00:36:05,563 --> 00:36:07,264
Ready?

295
00:36:11,769 --> 00:36:15,805
<i>[ Train Whistle Blowing ]</i>

296
00:36:15,807 --> 00:36:17,574
Oh!
[ Snickering ]

297
00:36:17,576 --> 00:36:19,776
That was horrible.
Why'd you show me that?

298
00:36:23,347 --> 00:36:24,814
Watch again.

299
00:36:26,384 --> 00:36:30,921
[ Train Whistle Blowing ]

300
00:36:30,923 --> 00:36:32,556
[ Groans ]

301
00:36:33,925 --> 00:36:36,960
See, this is good.

302
00:36:37,795 --> 00:36:39,462
