feel super puny.

323
00:38:33,911 --> 00:38:36,613
I don't know
why I thought
we'd be able to see it.

324
00:38:39,850 --> 00:38:44,487
I had a dream today
after we met.

325
00:38:44,489 --> 00:38:47,090
[ Clears Throat ]
I took a nap.

326
00:38:47,092 --> 00:38:48,958
We met today, right?

327
00:38:50,094 --> 00:38:54,397
So, uh, Barbra Streisand
was on Oprah,

328
00:38:54,399 --> 00:38:57,567
and she was crying,

329
00:38:57,569 --> 00:39:01,871
and...
she confessed to the world
that she had full-blown AIDS.

330
00:39:01,873 --> 00:39:03,540
And--
[ Laughs ]

331
00:39:06,711 --> 00:39:10,447
And Oprah took her hand,
and she said, "So do I."

332
00:39:10,449 --> 00:39:12,716
And they were both
just totally crying.

333
00:39:14,352 --> 00:39:16,586
And right after
she said it, she--

334
00:39:16,588 --> 00:39:19,022
She was crying so hard
that she farted.

335
00:39:20,558 --> 00:39:22,459
And I--

336
00:39:22,461 --> 00:39:25,028
