346
00:40:04,502 --> 00:40:06,035
Something from your niece.

347
00:40:07,438 --> 00:40:09,606
There's only one.
Do you wanna share it?

348
00:40:09,608 --> 00:40:11,174
Uh, yeah.

349
00:40:13,878 --> 00:40:15,712
