00:58:52,061 --> 00:58:54,296
Everyone's asking
about the computer.

461
00:58:54,298 --> 00:58:55,864
<i>[ Henry ]</i>
<i>Yeah.</i>

462
00:58:55,866 --> 00:58:57,533
<i>How's Karen?</i>

463
00:58:57,535 --> 00:58:59,234
