01:02:04,487 --> 01:02:08,223
I watched that damn thing
on there 20 times.

482
01:02:08,225 --> 01:02:10,392
Well, ours
is getting fixed.

483
01:02:11,728 --> 01:02:14,329
Just can't get it
out of my head.

484
01:02:14,331 --> 01:02:16,364
Why'd she let go?

485
01:02:16,366 --> 01:02:18,200
Yeah.

486
01:02:18,202 --> 01:02:20,469
Watching that stuff's
really addictive.

