01:02:21,938 --> 01:02:24,239
It's a huge problem
in China.

488
01:02:25,942 --> 01:02:28,143
Well, if it's
a huge problem in China,

489
01:02:29,278 --> 01:02:31,780
don't you think
it's a huge problem here?

490
01:02:35,785 --> 01:02:37,486
What'd you find?

491
01:02:37,488 --> 01:02:40,255
Oh, just a book
I lent him.

492
01:02:41,290 --> 01:02:43,925
It's good you guys read.

493
01:02:55,404 --> 01:02:57,272
Hey.

494
01:03:01,244 --> 01:03:03,345
He's good, right?

495
01:03:04,480 --> 01:03:06,548
Yeah.

496
01:03:12,789 --> 01:03:14,322
All right.

497
01:03:16,159 --> 01:03:18,360
To--
[ Sighs ]

498
01:03:21,430 --> 01:03:23,799
To--

499
01:03:23,801 --> 01:03:25,333
Oh, forget it.

500
01:03:25,335 --> 01:03:27,435
I hate toasts.
[ Chuckles ]
Yeah.

501
01:03:30,540 --> 01:03:32,307
No, I don't.

502
01:03:33,242 --> 01:03:34,509
To--

503
01:03:36,379 --> 01:03:38,446
I know.

504
01:03:43,486 --> 01:03:46,087
