505
01:03:46,089 --> 01:03:49,157
of our forgotten ancestors.

506
01:03:51,460 --> 01:03:53,929
Stop.

507
01:03:59,001 --> 01:04:01,069
Stop saying
good things.

508
01:04:03,272 --> 01:04:06,608
"Stop saying good things."
