510
01:04:09,012 --> 01:04:10,846
[ Laughs ]

511
01:04:20,156 --> 01:04:23,358
You'd never guess
where I was gonna be
a year ago today.

512
01:04:26,362 --> 01:04:29,431
You'd never guess
where I was gonna be.

513
01:04:30,499 --> 01:04:32,500
I'd never lie to you.

514
01:04:43,112 --> 01:04:45,013
[ Sighs ]

515
01:04:45,015 --> 01:04:46,982
[ Angela Mutters ]
Oh, God.

516
01:04:56,158 --> 01:04:58,660
[ Angela ]
Uh, Ben?

517
01:05:00,329 --> 01:05:02,130
I told you they...

518
01:05:02,132 --> 01:05:03,932
took my mom.

519
01:05:13,476 --> 01:05:16,311
I tri-- I--
I tried to get them...

520
01:05:16,313 --> 01:05:18,013
to take her.

521
01:05:18,981 --> 01:05:21,416
I did. I--

522
01:05:21,418 --> 01:05:23,551
I--

523
01:05:24,620 --> 01:05:27,622
I tried to--
[ Trembling ]

524
01:05:30,526 --> 01:05:32,560
Please.

525
01:06:01,657 --> 01:06:03,325
[ Whispers ]
Close to you.

526
01:06:04,093 --> 01:06:06,194
No. Not now.

527
01:06:10,132 --> 01:06:13,335
[ Both Grunting ]

528
01:06:41,430 --> 01:06:44,566
[ Moaning, Panting ]

529
01:06:44,568 --> 01:06:46,634
Don't stop.

530
01:06:48,738 --> 01:06:50,739
Yes. Yes.

531
01:06:50,741 --> 01:06:53,641
Oh, Ben, m-make me--

532
01:06:53,643 --> 01:06:56,444
